<F P=102>   LD0105215294 Budapest Kossuth Radio Network in Hungarian 
2100 GMT 1 May 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD0105215294 </F>
<F P=104>  Budapest Kossuth Radio Network </F>
<F P=105>  Hungarian </F>


