  [Text] Regarding a recent report, according to which 
Defense Minister Valentin Aleksandrov will resign, today 
Minister Aleksandrov personally stated in the Konkurenti 
[Competitors] program of Khorizont Radio that he does not intend 
to resign unless Prime Minister Lyuben Berov asks him to. 

