<F P=100> CROATIA </F>
<H3> <TI>   Manolic Denies Meeting With Markovic </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Manolic Denies Meeting With Markovic </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD0205190394 Zagreb HTV Television in Serbo-Croatian 1730 
GMT 2 May 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD0205190394 </F>
<F P=104>  Zagreb HTV Television </F>
<F P=105>  Serbo-Croatian </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Josip Manolic has denied a Croatian TV report 
according to which he met Ante Markovic in Vienna on 28 April. 
In a statement issued by the office of the Croatian parliament's 
Chamber of Counties, Manolic says: I have not met Mr. Markovic 
in Vienna or any other place in the period mentioned in the 
report. 

</TEXT>

