  [Excerpts] The situation is once more worrying in Bosnia, 
particularly in Sarajevo and around Gorazde too where a UN 
Protection Forces [UNPROFOR] convoy is blocked by Serbs. This 
incident is reported to be very serious. Incidents are more and 
more frequent and cease-fires are no longer respected. [passage 
omitted] 
