captioned as UNPROFOR commander for Sarajevo sector] I have been 
hindered since the start of the Gorazde crisis. Our freedom of 
movement has been restricted. The tension provoked by the 
Gorazde crisis resulted in massive harassment by the Serb side. 
There were attempts to get more weapons through our sector by 
taking advantage of these difficulties. [end recording] 
